@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hugmpq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.cos((v2 + 0.92 * v2 + 0.60)) * (wp.cos(v2 + 0.07) * (tmp + 0.96 - v1 + 0.11)))
    v0 = ((v0 - wp.exp(v1 + 0.64)) - (wp.exp(v2 + 0.48) * (v1 + 0.77 * tmp + 0.78)))
    v1 = (v2 / (0.70 / wp.cos(v1 + 0.57)))
    v1 = wp.exp(tmp)
    v0 = (0.91 + v1)
    data[tid] = v0
